  m_OnCullStateChanged:
    m_PersistentCalls:
      m_Calls: []
  m_text: 'Gameplay:

    Goal: Defeat all dragons to progress to the next level,
    without running out of mana.


    Dragons will be surrounded by blocks of varying
    strength to protect them, glass, wood, stone, and metal. (That also the order
    of increasing strength)


    Levels are chosen randomly, and the game ends when
    all levels are cleared, or you run out of mana before clearning all the dragons.


    There
    will be poitions that will increase mana, decrease mana, or randomly do one.'
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 8f586378b4e144a9851e7b34d9b748ee, type: 2}
